## EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

A premium, immersive, section-based wedding invitation website continuing the Royal Midnight Rajasthan visual language from the Save The Date video. The experience feels like walking through a Rajasthani palace — deep midnight blue backgrounds, antique matte gold accents, cinematic animations, and interactive click-to-proceed navigation across 6 full-viewport "rooms."

**Template Scope:** This is a frontend-only invitation template. No backend, admin panel, or database. After development, it integrates into the platform where all backend systems (RSVP tracking, guest management, analytics) are already available. Focus is 100% on design, animations, and user experience.

**Core Experience:**

- 6 sections (0-5), each a full-viewport room — click to proceed, no scrolling
- Curtain reveal opens to Lord Ganesha with shlok (content pre-rendered behind curtain)
- Palace doors swing open to reveal hero screen (content pre-rendered behind doors)
- Self-contained royal scroll event cards with venue + address + map in each card
- Floating marigold petals + diya lighting create living palace atmosphere
- Heartbeat countdown glow + confetti RSVP celebration
- Guest personalization via URL parameter
- Mobile-first — 80%+ guests via WhatsApp on mobile

