### Gold Shimmer Text Effect (Matte Antique)

Applied to couple names (4s loop) and section headings (6s loop). CSS `background-clip: text` with animated linear gradient. Gradient: `#8B7340 → #C9A96E → #D4B87A → #C9A96E → #8B7340`. `background-size: 200% 100%`. MATTE feel only — no sparkle, no glitter, no bright flashes. Fallback: static `#C9A96E`.

