## SECTION STRUCTURE (6 Sections)

```
Section 0: Lord Ganesha ── Curtain Reveal (content behind) ──▶
Section 1: Opening Hero ── Palace Door Opening (content behind) ──▶
Section 2: Wedding Celebrations ── Fade + gold sweep ──▶
Section 3: Gallery ── Soft cross-fade ──▶
Section 4: Countdown + Blessings ── Smooth fade-in ──▶
Section 5: RSVP & Contact ── Golden reveal
```

| Section | Name | Navigation Button | Transition In |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 0 | Lord Ganesha | "शुभ आरंभ · Begin" (appears after shlok) | Curtain reveal (content behind) |
| 1 | Opening Screen | "View Celebrations →" (appears after names animate) | Palace door opening (content behind) |
| 2 | Wedding Celebrations | "Next: Gallery →" (always visible) | Fade + gold particle sweep |
| 3 | Gallery | "Next: Countdown →" (appears after gallery loads) | Soft cross-fade + gold shimmer |
| 4 | Countdown + Blessings | "Next: RSVP →" (appears after countdown loads) | Smooth fade-in from bottom |
| 5 | RSVP & Contact | "Accept Invitation" (FINAL action — gold filled primary button) | Golden reveal sweep |

**Persistent Global Elements (all sections):** Floating marigold petals, diya icon on headings, floating nav menu (6 items), music toggle, progress dots (6 dots, desktop only).

